1498  // make sure the solution is the same across all nodes
1499  // ignore ghost nodes

1501  errorVal = std::fabs(solution-finalSolution[i]);
1502  if (errorVal > 1.e-4) {
1503  steady=false;
1504  std::cout << "Inconsistent steady solution at i=" << i << std::endl;
1505  std::cout << "Got " << finalSolution[i] << " Expected " << solution << std::endl;
1506  }
1507  }
1508  result.UpdateResult("SteadySolver:Works",steady);
1509  }

1932  " Expected " << solution << std::endl;
1933  }
1934  }
1935  result.UpdateResult("SolverForwardEuler:Works",steady);
1936  }
